Hello and welcome to my profile!
All my vehicles are self-owned and thoroughly maintained between my son and I. We are car enthusiasts and hope to rent to people that feel the same. Our small fleet is based in Vancouver WA and is community driven, renting to both local people as well as people coming in from out of town.

While we have always had a love for cars whether luxury, classic, or exotic we never thought we would be able to obtain our own as well as share the opportunity to enjoy them with others. As we add to our collection, we offer you the same excitement. Oregon summers and Arizona winters provide the perfect environment to cruise through the desert or mountains in an exhilarating, exotic, performance machine. Our fleet includes a 2019 Lamborghini Huracan Performante, 2018 McLaren 720S, 2018 Audi R8, 2023 Corvette Z06 C8, 2023 Corvette C8 Stingray, 2021 Mercedes Benz G-Wagon AMG G63. Please feel free to reach out at rental@fisherluxuryrental.com for additional information. we are looking forward to adding more variety soon! Depending on if you want to take a fun drive into the sunset, have a creative photo shoot, drive up to Hood River, or go to dinner and park in front for VIP treatment we have several options to suit your event or mood. Please take a look and follow on Instagram @Fisherluxuryrental
